<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.11">
<l>cōrāta vepporuṭku mātiyāñ cōtikkē</l>
<l>yārāta kātal kurukūrc caṭakōpa</l>
<l>ṉōrā yirañcoṉṉa vavaṟṟu ḷivaippattuñ</l>
<l>cōrār viṭārkkaṇṭīr vaikuntan tiṇṇeṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who don’t tire</l>
<l>of these ten among the one thousand spoken</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr in insatiable love</l>
<l>for our unwearying treasure, for the light that is the beginning,</l>
	<l>will firmly not be released from Vaikuntam, you see.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
